import logo from './logo.svg';
import './App.css';
import ProductCard from './Container/Productcard/Productcard.js';
import ProductCustomizationDrawer from './Container/ProductCustomizationDrawer/ProductCustomizationDrawer.js';
import DrawerComp from './Components/DrawerComp/DrawerComp';
import { background } from '@chakra-ui/styled-system';
import {
  Drawer,
  DrawerBody,
  DrawerFooter,
  DrawerOverlay,
  DrawerContent,
  DrawerCloseButton,
  useDisclosure,
  DrawerHeader ,
  Flex, Box, Spacer, Text, Stack, Radio, RadioGroup,CheckboxGroup,Checkbox,
} from "@chakra-ui/react"
import { ArrowBackIcon } from '@chakra-ui/icons'

function App() {
  return (
    <>
    <ProductCard/>
    <ProductCard/>
    <ProductCard/>
    <ProductCard/>
    <ProductCard/>
    <DrawerComp
     placement={'bottom'} 
     bg="black"
     height="85vh"
     borderTopRightRadius='30px' 
     borderTopLeftRadius="30px"
    >
      <>
       <DrawerHeader bg="black" borderTopRightRadius="30px" borderTopLeftRadius="30px"   borderBottomWidth="1px">
       <Flex direction="column" mt="16px" mr="33px" mb="12px">
            <Flex>
              <ArrowBackIcon w="20px" alignSelf="flex-end" color="white" />
              <Text ml="10px" color="white" lineHeight="19px" fontSize="16px" fontWeight="bold">{'Mc Aloo tikki'}</Text>
              <Box ml="10px" w="8px" h="8px" mb="10px" border="1px solid #E11010">
                <Box m="0.8px" mt="0.9px" w="4.4px" h="4.4px" bg="#EC1010" />
              </Box>
            </Flex>
            <Text ml="30px" mt="10px" fontSize="14px" lineHeight="17px" fontSize="14px" color="white" >₹{'25'}</Text>
          </Flex>
          </DrawerHeader>
          <DrawerBody>
          <Flex direction="column">
            <Box>
              <Text my="15px" fontWeight="extrabold">SELECT ANY ONE</Text>
              <RadioGroup defaultValue="1">
                <Stack>
                  <Radio value="1" colorScheme="green">Checked </Radio>
                  <Radio value="2" colorScheme="green">Unchecked</Radio>
                  <Radio value="3" colorScheme="green">Unchecked</Radio>
                </Stack>
              </RadioGroup>
            </Box>
            <Box>
              <Text my="15px" fontWeight="extrabold">SELECT THE  TOPPINGS</Text>
              <CheckboxGroup colorScheme="green" defaultValue={["naruto", "kakashi"]}>
                <Stack>
                  <Checkbox value="naruto">Naruto</Checkbox>
                  <Checkbox value="sasuke">Sasuke</Checkbox>
                  <Checkbox value="kakashi">kakashi</Checkbox>
                </Stack>
              </CheckboxGroup>
            </Box>
            <Box>
              <Text my="15px" fontWeight="extrabold">SELECT ANY ONE</Text>
              <RadioGroup defaultValue="1">
                <Stack>
                  <Radio value="1" colorScheme="green">Checked </Radio>
                  <Radio value="2" colorScheme="green">Unchecked</Radio>
                  <Radio value="3" colorScheme="green">Unchecked</Radio>
                </Stack>
              </RadioGroup>
            </Box>
          </Flex>
          </DrawerBody>
          </>
    </DrawerComp>
    {/* <ProductCustomizationDrawer/> */}
    </>

  );
}

export default App;
